snippet.title: Hacker's Adventure-MOBILE GAME(NEW TRAILER)
snippet.description:
The world's first hacker-themed platform game.

---Play Store Download Link---

https://play.google.com/store/apps/de...

Get ready for a breathtaking adventure.Help Super Hacker collect high-tech products.

Features:

-10x3 handcrafted adventure levels
-3 different season 
-Game style evolving from easy to difficult
-special hacker power

---------NOTICE---------
The necessary citations for the images used in the icon and photos are given in the game.

Nefes kesen bir maceraya hazır olun.Super Hacker'ın yüksek teknoloji ürünleri toplamasına yardımcı olun.

Özellikler:

-10x3 el yapımı macera seviyeleri
-3 farklı sezon
-Kolaydan zora gelişen oyun tarzı
-özel hacker elektrik yetenegi

---Music---- 
Drolood - Break It [NCS Release]
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QW7e4JJwy0Q
